name: RABID
description:
The impulses are excruciatingly pleasurable, like dynamite being lit, so is the passion of my crave.
This is the second piece of this series called "YOURS TRULY " This series was created to pay homage to the material plane, it's creator, the human perception that surrounds it and the dark aesthetic art that is consumed by it. You can follow this love story on twitter @0yourstruly9 this is a #fear4hen offering
